s/2021/10/1022-5a-1-582x580.jpg 582w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1022-5a-1-902x900.jpg 902w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1022-5a-1-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1022-5a-1-768x766.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1022-5a-1-1536x1532.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1022-5a-1.jpg 1540w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 582px" /></a></p><p>雖然 Netflix 考慮為《魷魚遊戲》推出遊戲，但至今尚未成事，官方亦沒有推出過任何劇集相關的手機程式。Stefanko 分析了 Google Play Store 現時超過 200 款與《魷魚遊戲》有關的程式，暫時只發現一款內藏惡意程式碼，經報告後 Google 亦已經將之下架。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://designtaxi.com/news/416307/Beware-Squid-Game-Malware-Infiltrates-Phones-With-Fake-Wallpapers/">designtaxi</a></p>
